      "comment": "THREEEYEDWITCH (4) started at odds on debut but ran a bold race, finishing second beaten 3 lengths over 1110m at Doomben. Had trialled well at Doomben and is well placed to go one better. Has an inside gate and a handy 1.5kg claim. NAUGHTY NEIL (3) was well in the market on debut last time out and ran well but found a couple better over 1110m at Doomben. Open to improvement and with a 2kg claimer aboard today and is a serious contender. FINAL EDIT (1) debuts with the blinkers on. Maps well and his latest trial suggests he'll be very competitive. The 2kg claim assists as well. HANG UP (8) resumes with two trials under the saddle. Expect her to come back better. MISHANI HONOUR (2) will be fitter and should be around the mark.",
